### Todo API — Coleção de Requisições
### Use com a extensão REST Client (VS Code) ou importe no Insomnia

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ─────────────────────────────
### AUTH
### ─────────────────────────────

### Registrar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Meus dados
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### PROJETOS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar projetos (público, com paginação)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?page=1&limit=10

### Buscar com filtro
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?search=api

### Criar projeto
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Projeto Alpha",
  "description": "Descrição do projeto"
}

### Buscar projeto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI

### Atualizar projeto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Título Atualizado"
}

### Deletar projeto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### TAREFAS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar tarefas do projeto
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI/tasks

### Criar tarefa
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implementar autenticação",
  "description": "JWT + bcrypt",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Atualizar status da tarefa
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI/tasks/TASK_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DONE"
}

### Deletar tarefa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/PROJECT_ID_AQUI/tasks/TASK_ID_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### ADMIN
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar todos os usuários (ADMIN only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
